Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.64,0:27:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人类要真正长大…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所必须经过的仪式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.60,0:27:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 没想到她居然会临阵脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.72,0:27:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离空间跳跃临界 1.5 1.2
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.70,0:27:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提督 变动重力源即将进行空间跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.88,0:27:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.24,0:27:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.36,0:27:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺诺！
